Package: container-python-full-@{PYTHON_BASE_VERSION}
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: allowed
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         container-python-@{PYTHON_BASE_VERSION} (= ${binary:Version}),
         container-python-dev-@{PYTHON_BASE_VERSION} (= ${binary:Version}),
Suggests: ca-certificates,
Provides: ${pip:autolist},
Description: Python v@{PYTHON_BASE_VERSION} - full package
 Python is a high-level, interactive, object-oriented language.
 Its v@{PYTHON_BASE_VERSION} version includes an extensive class library
 with lots of goodies for network programming, system administration,
 sounds and graphics.
 .
 This package contains Python package manager "pip" besides packages
 "setuptools" and "wheel".

